<item>
            <title>[LU-1435] failure on mmp.sh, test_8 &quot;Device or resource busy&quot; / mount /dev/lvm-MDS/P1 on mds1 should fail&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1435</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a64943a0-a51c-11e1-adce-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a64943a0-a51c-11e1-adce-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_8 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Starting mds1: -o user_xattr,acl  /dev/lvm-MDS/P1 /mnt/mds1&lt;br/&gt;
client-30vm3: e2fsck 1.41.90.wc4 (01-Sep-2011)&lt;br/&gt;
client-30vm3: e2fsck: Device or resource busy while trying to open /dev/lvm-MDS/P1&lt;br/&gt;
Filesystem mounted or opened exclusively by another program?&lt;br/&gt;
Started lustre-MDT0000&lt;br/&gt;
 mmp test_8: @@@@@@ FAIL: mount /dev/lvm-MDS/P1 on mds1 should fail&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: mmp 8&lt;/p&gt;</description>
